{
  "texts": [
    "We make the reasonable assumption that the training dataset will not be filtered to ensure maximum safety due to the prohibitive compute cost.",
    "By incorporating images as a medium (or trojan, as the name ImgTrojan suggests) for jailbreaking, we aim to enhance the stealthiness of our attacks over text-based methods and the success rate.",
    "Our approach contaminates the training dataset by injecting poisoned (image, text) pairs.",
    "These pairs replace the original textual captions with malicious JBPs.",
    "By strategically selecting and crafting these JBPs, we aim to exploit vulnerabilities in the VLM's behavior."
  ]
}